definitions.definition: The act of throwing or darting out with a sudden force and rapid flight.
The uttering of a short, sudden exclamation or prayer , or the exclamation or prayer uttered.
The act of ejecting or suddenly throwing, as a fluid from a duct or other body structure.

subdefinitions.definition: A reflex in human beings and other mammals in response to sexual stimulation involving the forcible ejection from the urethra of, in males, semen ; and, in females, vaginal fluid .

main_definition: The act of throwing or darting out with a sudden force and rapid flight.
secondary_definitions: The uttering of a short, sudden exclamation or prayer , or the exclamation or prayer uttered.
( biology ) The act of ejecting or suddenly throwing, as a fluid from a duct or other body structure.
